parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can lead to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates without manual force
surges forward
or accelerates suddenly
even when the brakes are applied.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cruise control malfunctions can lead to unintended acceleration, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates or decelerates without manual input while using cruise control
or the cruise control fails to disengage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can lead to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The brakes fail to engage or are ineffective
causing the vehicle to accelerate or fail to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Accelerator pedal malfunctions can lead to unintended acceleration, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: The accelerator pedal sticks or fails to return to its normal position
causing the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sticky/melting dashboard can cause glare on the windshield, impairing the driver's visibility and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard feels sticky or soft to the touch
has a shiny or glossy appearance
and causes glare on the windshield
especially during sunny or nighttime driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine and transmission issues can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine dies or stalls
the check engine light and stability control light come on
the vehicle has difficulty shifting gears
and the transmission slips or hesitates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting and sticky dashboard can cause a glare on the windshield, obstructing the driver's vision and creating a hazardous driving condition. It can also lead to eye strain, headaches, and accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard feels sticky to the touch
has a shiny and reflective surface
and creates a glare on the windshield. Bugs and dust particles stick to the dashboard
making it difficult to clean. The dashboard may also emit a strong
unpleasant odor.
